MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 12e78ffe3bd9a4bfb86c2e60065daca2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Level2Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - Yo bro! I'm gonna beat you bro! You suck!
  - "There is a universe in which I win instantly! \nAnd that universe is this one!"
  - "I dost the chosen one selected by the mandate of heaven \nto smite mortals such
    as thou."
  - "Know thou well thy ordained station, else shall I, \nby sovereign hand and stern
    necessity, consign thee unto it \nwith most resolute authority."
  - "Let us, therefore, in the dread convulsion of ire most unbridled, and amidst
    the \ntumultuous clangor of arms and the dolorous wailing of spirits affronted,
    forthwith engage in mortal contention, \nwherein our sinews, hitherto steadfast,
    shall be rent asunder, our very essences laid bare \nto the inexorable judgment
    of Fate herself, who, from her empyreal throne, doth gaze with unblinking and
    austere \ncountenance upon the chaos and devastation wrought by our own ungoverned
    hands, \nwhilst the firmament above,"
  - ' shaken and perturbed by the resonance of our unmitigated fury, recoils and
    trembles, and time itself, being but a frail witness to the enormity of our strife,
    doth falter and stagger beneath the intolerable weight of our unrelenting and
    interminable combat.'
